gned><lb/><handShift scribe="#pmb2173"/>O. S.</closer><p><handShift scribe="#pmb2121"/><rs ref="#pmb30233" type="work"><hi rend="latintype">Charolais</hi></rs> wird im Herb<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t in <rs ref="#pmb36300" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Kopenhagen</hi></rs> aufgeführt.</p></div></body></text></TEI>